Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.20,0:00:55.50,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}現在也毫無疑問
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.50,0:00:57.66,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}在我心中迴盪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.25,0:00:59.88,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}踏上同一條旅途
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.88,0:01:01.96,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}明明沒什麼特別的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.96,0:01:03.59,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}卻讓我眼角含淚
